{
  "stem": "23131.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I sat down, my father was by neighbor, so that I had to open the door, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was playing [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother went to visit, to pay a shiva call, to this druggist that he was very good friends with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a tragical story there, and that's why-- and my mother was so involved in it, because the mo-- they had a only daughter, and the daughter married somebody they didn't approve of it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And mother told her, if you marry him, no matter how I'm shivaing over you, will find me dead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because she wasn't a wealthy-- a healthy woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She married and mother died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my mother went to pay the druggist a shiva call.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was sitting home and doing-- took out my books and the phone rang.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I knew that nobody would call me, because there weren't any phones besides the druggist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sure enough, it was the druggist called me, saying come fast for the doctor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Mommy's not feeling well, and it's very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "As she walked into the house-- you know, you don't say anything when you walk into a shiva house-- she sat down on the step-- on the chair.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The druggist was sitting the shiva, and she fell off the chair and that was it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was on my birthday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, I called right away my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will never forget, our doctor-- which it was a doctor, not a specialist, like today for every little thing is a specialist.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was a doctor for everything-- for head and feet and hands and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
